  <brief_title>S0508: Thalidomide and Temozolomide in Treating Patients With Stage IV Melanoma That Cannot Be Removed By Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Trial of Combination Thalidomide Plus Temozolomide in Patients With Metastatic Malignant Melanoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
